thread.title: L D

author: L D
title: L D
text: I signed up to this site for a free account, seeking a place room to rent. They with withheld the messages sent to me by people looking for tenants for 2 weeks! Needless to say, the rooms were filled before I even received the messages. Waste of time. Stick with Gumtree. I can understand charging people to advertise their rooms, but how are they going to find tenants if if your going to pull these kind of stunts with out warning? Forget this site.
